value:
"/root/.ssh/id_rsa":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0600'
  content: <%= @host.params['id_dsa'] %>
"/root/.ssh/id_rsa.pub":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0644'
  content: <%= !@host.params['id_dsa.pub'].empty? && @host.params['id_dsa.pub'].split(@host.shortname + ": ").size > 1 ? @host.params['id_dsa.pub'].split(@host.shortname + ": ")[1].split("\n")[0] : "" %>
"/root/.ssh/known_hosts":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0644'
"/home/ksfuser/.ssh/id_rsa.pub":
  ensure: file
  owner: 'ksfuser'
  group: 'ksfuser'
  mode: '0644'
  content: "ssh-rsa  ksfuser@foundation"
